Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優真是的  快點換衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別吵  等吃完抹茶麵包再換也來得及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抹茶麵包什麼的邊走邊吃也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在路上吃東西也太沒教養了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的也對啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我們做點有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  優還沒換好衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還想上一節體育課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且學校也禁止穿運動服回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就這樣穿著回家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現了就慘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  別人也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但就因為小優所以大家都回不去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:40.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}雫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下…你在寫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正好想去自動售貨機那邊一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,楓跟我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}偷瞄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好可以一邊吃一邊等小柚她們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就來幫你換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我先吃完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂動  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛呢  小春春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了琴音她們還在教室裡…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我想脫她衣服來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脫衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的！春香！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是快換衣服啊  別老顧著玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了小優我才能得救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差點就溺水了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去像是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優不是說過嗎  要是我溺水的話就會來救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個意思啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救人？發生了什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,注意不要受傷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學穿著泳裝的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會長也會一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得偶爾來一次也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不是因為這是個監視春香和優的好機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們給我等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐不會游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:46.51,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「泳裝殺必死☆還有走光喲」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:46.51,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「泳裝殺必死☆還有走光喲」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  優
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我…我的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去找回來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉…掉哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你先上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起眼鏡  這次你把更重要的東西給丟掉了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家玩得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很開心哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室內泳池還算可以湊合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡有泳池真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是琴音同學為我們準備的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  所以請盡情地玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平時看起來是那樣  其實她可是名流哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接著！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  為什麼文化祭的慶祝會要在恒溫泳池裡開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽你這麼一說我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是小雫的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…因為游泳可以減肥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也只是動動身體而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不過你卻在喝東西的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要準備場地太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去游一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…請問美月會長也不會游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學向我搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其…其實不會游泳也沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來呢  我想給美月會長和小春春進行特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個的話就不會怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這個比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是請您換回剛才的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香又自己一個人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫也一起下去游泳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是敏感膚質
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的皮膚太敏感了  所以要小心一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不對  小春春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打水可是最基礎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長也是  看來還需要大量訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來來  不會游泳的都來這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音教練看著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就湊巧瞥了一眼吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實不會游泳也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來幹勁不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  請幫我把那個東西拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼東西被推過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是山田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山田小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有鈴木小姐  田中小姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰學會了游泳就把這個獎勵給她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會因為這種東西而開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加速了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著山田過來一看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是琴音姐姐回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那個女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是琴音的那個還在讀小學的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家已經上初一了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雫  果然就是你讓姐姐住自己家去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是琴音自己說想住過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能  不要胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想起來從以前開始琴音姐姐就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要這個人一過來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐就會總是…總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  別玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總是把欺負的對象從我變成她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  琴音姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽對你擅自離家的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是非常生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且連婚約的事情都被你放到一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音姐姐今天必須搬回家裡住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別用你濕漉漉的手碰我的恰比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音真的覺得這樣無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不是很清楚具體情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是琴音看起來並不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫你覺得沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她一直待在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也無法讓她幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的有合適的對象的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是應該去好好面對他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我當作你的避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再那麼隨便地親我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你說的都是真心話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會把琴音姐姐交給你這種人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先來比一場再說怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人還在練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢  小忍和小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰贏了琴音就住誰家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳比賽是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山田  現在就去把我的泳衣拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我有件事一直瞞著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經準備完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼背後要捆個布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它是恰比！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恰比可是很擅長狗爬式的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和恰比是一心同體的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這場比賽我贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長還真信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小雫  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒因為剛才那個感到高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  琴音你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勝者  小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恰比吸水後會變得那麼重是不是有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是做了什麼  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道山田小姐是為了琴音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柚你真淡定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明剛才的修羅場還是挺慘烈的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢  我蠻動搖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫剛才有說接吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定之前說的吻臉頰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是楓  想像力有夠豐富的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能比那個還過的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
