Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好帶圍巾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優從後面抱緊我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,流鼻涕了  難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.68,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,765)}「和小優去購物」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.68,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,765)}「和小優去購物」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明帶條圍巾什麼的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有  但是送人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送…送人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看不見前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優  你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人好像在找小優  不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐有圍巾  不用你給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  原來是美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個  優  你這樣會感冒的吧  拿去繫好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那麼排斥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是考生  如果感冒就糟糕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,語氣好假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那姐姐就先走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這麼討厭這條圍巾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒  優用剩下的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是姐姐用剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一次都沒有圍過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是小優的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是用剩下的所以你才不願意圍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我用的那條圍巾已經破舊不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後姐姐就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的  你用這條吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在店裡看見條不錯的還打算買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過為了姐姐的好意  你就用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要勤儉節約啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給春香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安莫寧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫寧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優帶來了個可疑分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生物課的作業做了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無視我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天想要去買條新的圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經決定好目標了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要買條軟綿綿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我想要的那條
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小雫有的話也就意味著…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得挺可愛於是昨天去買了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是最後一條所以就豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫從昨天開始就一直在鏡子前面欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛  你有種就別看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒貨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  那今天放學後去找條更好看的圍巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要那條
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那條已經被小雫買走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非那條不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  陪我去買東西
